{"tid":511961,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BTS V奪2017世界百大靚仔冠軍，鐘鉉進榜「RIP」悼念","createTime":"2017-12-28T03:58:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-28T08:08:05.000Z","uid":60286,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4f384fca795e426879a37285e248eb788c0d4761","tid":511961,"uid":60286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T03:58:00.000Z","msg":"美國電影網站「TC Candler」公佈今年的世界百大帥哥排行榜，南韓防彈少年團成員V名次大躍進，從去年的第60名衝上冠軍，去年的「亞洲最帥」BIGBANG主唱太陽跌出前10名，亞、季軍為美國男星Jason Momoa及Armie Hammer。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/28/115612_2e932eca6e4ad3f9ee60718992cc9510.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F28%2F115612_2e932eca6e4ad3f9ee60718992cc9510.jpg&h=2225ccfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nV<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/28/115638_e270928ffbb6b8ebe831fb484aa531cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F28%2F115638_e270928ffbb6b8ebe831fb484aa531cb.jpg&h=77418329&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJason Momoa<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/28/115648_078c93aa9bd7291f54b98f8890f1f459.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F28%2F115648_078c93aa9bd7291f54b98f8890f1f459.jpg&h=2043f627&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nArmie Hammer<br />\n<br />\n「TC Candler」從1990年舉辦「世界百大帥哥、美女」排行榜，除了從外表進行評選，並以文化背景、生活模式、公眾意見等多面向，選出「世界百大帥哥、美女」，榜單歷史至今已超過25年。月中驟逝的「SHINee」鐘鉉奪下第27名，「TC Candler」特地在照片下方寫有「REST IN PEACE」悼念他，而台灣男星高以翔則從去年第7名下滑至第21名，「GOT7」中的台裔美籍成員Mark則獲得第70名。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/28/115524_87f2242bbcac91b663c4c6f987e4dd5e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F28%2F115524_87f2242bbcac91b663c4c6f987e4dd5e.jpg&h=32044bc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鐘鉉位列第27名。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/28/115542_5d167a406965e60891933edddaa73aaf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F28%2F115542_5d167a406965e60891933edddaa73aaf.jpg&h=61d3535b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高以翔再次進榜。<br />\n<br />\n此外，其他上榜的日韓男星包括「EXO」世勳（第9名）、「防彈少年團」柾國（第13名）、「BIGBANG」太陽（第19名）、南柱赫（第23名）、「GOT7」Jackson（第35名）、「EXO」KAI（第38名）、「SUPER JUNIOR」始源（第40名）、寺田拓哉（第42名）、「KARD」BM（第47名）、「SEVENTEEN」玟奎（第49名）、「防彈少年團」智旻（第64名）、赤西仁 （第66名）、「SEVENTEEN」圓佑（第72名）、山崎賢人（第81名）、李敏鎬（第84名）、岩田剛典（第96名）、「NCT」泰容（第99名）。"},{"pid":"5fd7bbe6a2ad3d22b6538539e94b48165f0c1d08","tid":511961,"uid":60286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T07:41:44.000Z","msg":"冇連登男神金城武、彭于晏<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa63c644f44d06ebba7a81815583d0873af80826","tid":511961,"uid":4051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T07:50:34.000Z","msg":"等睇第7名今晚出片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38cf07c83696b611675c7b2bdeeba265fa71efe7","tid":511961,"uid":23021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa63c644f44d06ebba7a81815583d0873af80826","tid":511961,"uid":4051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T07:50:34.000Z","msg":"等睇第7名今晚出片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T07:56:20.000Z","msg":"出唔出到10分鐘呀"},{"pid":"99bd87b53f3689987dedcbd98f758989231e5812","tid":511961,"uid":138557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T08:02:32.000Z","msg":"升同跌嘅原因係咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b8a308e1f8158d9a1e1197d9fc4d45f0edbe0cc","tid":511961,"uid":60286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T08:06:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ojVQQBiwono\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FojVQQBiwono&d=3Q0axaAZ8itZuAOIHRvp%2Fb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=f7e4c883\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ojVQQBiwono</a>"},{"pid":"d93db6a72a4494e1406073fccf51f986622eb7db","tid":511961,"uid":139815,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T08:08:05.000Z","msg":"連登一眾巴打<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/28/160729_6dc42f871c6e48eab35529f5780b38de.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F28%2F160729_6dc42f871c6e48eab35529f5780b38de.jpg&h=addf66d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">排名:第1 (2017年new)</span></span>"}]}